### Base URL
@baseURL = http://localhost:3000/api/todos

### Get all todos
GET {{baseURL}}

### Create a new todo
POST {{baseURL}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Learn GORM",
  "description": "Understand how to integrate GORM with Go",
  "priority": 1,
  "completed": false,
  "dueDate": "2023-12-31T00:00:00Z",
  "createdAt": "...",
  "updatedAt": "..."
}

### Update a specific todo
PUT {{baseURL}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Mastering Go",
  "completed": true
}

### Delete a specific todo
DELETE {{baseURL}}/{id}